To consider operation period for SLA calculations
e.g. SR is created at 1/1/xxxx 3:00 PM and SLA is configured as 1 business day. Then if this flag is checked, SR Expected datetime will be set to 1/2/xxxx 11:59 PM instead of 1/2/xxxx 3:00 PM.
